HEADWORD: Horsenail
<hw>Horse"nail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A thin, pointed
nail, with a heavy flaring head, for securing a horseshoe to the hoof; a
horseshoe nail.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

